Network scanning - actively utilizing network technologies to gathern info about technologies that are running in the network. Discover live hosts on the network.

Host discovery is network scanning, Discover live hosts on the network.

Port scan 
Service scan to verify port scan

Vulnerability scanning - not a network scan, can be an agent installed in the host 

What's hosts are alive? what are they running? what are the vulnerabilities?

Port scan - what ports are running
Service scan - verity what service is running in that port and the version of the service that is running

